Several of the names of the Mayors have been supplied from a list of Mayors in Greaves papers (4770, page 3 sqq.), which begins in 1410. Greaves only gives the names of the Mayors. Names inserted in the following List solely upon Greaves’ authority are distinguished by an asteris-k (ᾗ). The numbers of Burgesses enrolled in different years have also been derived from Greaves.
